{"tid":2392393,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"獲女友鞭策下體能提升 洪永成笑稱：有進步囉！","createTime":"2021-02-02T18:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:51:08.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15c3015432bc0e3e73ef6fa09c087f731fc10f98","tid":2392393,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T18:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9z5e95i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9z5e95i.jpg&h=4278f91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs-orientalsunday-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1232112312321_3219972885c3c5f3ddd654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs-orientalsunday-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F1232112312321_3219972885c3c5f3ddd654.jpg&h=9edb1046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洪永城（Tony）在宣傳新劇《陀槍師姐2021》孭起鄧佩儀時「紅都面晒」，他笑言對方望落輕磅，實則骨重，加上自己年紀不輕，又少吃補腰藥，難免有點吃力。Tony又指平時是女友梁諾妍（Inez）孭他，皆因對方是運動健將，他在女友鞭策下，體能節節上升，打算年底跟女友跑半馬拉松。笑問女友有否讚他「勁咗」？他笑說：「OK啦！有進步囉！」<br />\n<br />\n談到Inez明天生日，Tony表示已預留整天陪女友，又笑說：「連荷里活大片找我試鏡都不去呀！活動已安排了，禮物也買好。（送戒指嗎？）不是啦！總之是貼身又貼心。」"},{"pid":"a4c73e992bff6354e6b2a0026a1d5df0cc2eb9b6","tid":2392393,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />m男"},{"pid":"d54de3591acfe08e8b8e754c68ea1df1a1986cc2","tid":2392393,"uid":34553,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"下體應該好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鞭到腫撚晒"},{"pid":"d62cb49cdeb39f60ed91f57a54831df248205ecf","tid":2392393,"uid":23445,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"下體能提升<i